ọọki rẹ le farahan.','Pages'=>'Àwọn Ojú-ìwé','Choose in which pages your blocks can be displayed.'=>'Yan níbi tí àwọn bulọọki rẹ le han.','Browser & Device'=>'Báwọ & Ẹrọ','Choose which browsers and devices can see your blocks.'=>'Yan ẹniti awọn báwọ ati awọn ẹrọ le rii awọn bulọọki rẹ.','Operating System'=>'Eto Isẹ','Choose which operating systems can see your blocks.'=>'Yan awọn eto isẹ tí le rii awọn bulọọki rẹ.','Cookie'=>'Kuki','Show or hide blocks based on cookie values.'=>'Fihan tàbí pa àwọn bulọọki da lori iye kuki.','User Meta'=>'Meta Olumulo','Show or hide blocks based on user meta values.'=>'Fihan tàbí pa àwọn bulọọki da lori iye meta olumulo.','Post Meta'=>'Meta Ifiweranṣẹ','Show or hide blocks based on post meta values.'=>'Fihan tàbí pa àwọn bulọọki da lori iye meta ifiweranṣẹ.','Query String'=>'Ọrọ ìbéèrè','Show or hide blocks based on URL query parameters.'=>'Fihan tàbí pa àwọn bulọọki da lori awọn paramita ìbéèrè URL.','Capabilities'=>'Agbara','Show or hide blocks based on user capabilities.'=>'Fihan tàbí pa àwọn bulọọki da lori awọn agbara olumulo.','Save Controls'=>'Fipamọ Àwọn Iṣakoso','Loading presets...'=>'Loading presets...','Accordion - PublishPress'=>'Accordion - PublishPress','Button - PublishPress'=>'Bọtini - PublishPress','Icon - PublishPress'=>'Aami - PublishPress','Image - PublishPress'=>'Aworan - PublishPress','List - PublishPress'=>'Atokọ - PublishPress','Table - PublishPress'=>'Tebulu - PublishPress','Tabs - PublishPress'=>'Tẹbẹs - PublishPress','Video - PublishPress'=>'Fidio - PublishPress','Columns - PublishPress'=>'Kólọmù - PublishPress','Column - PublishPress'=>'Kólọmù - PublishPress','Contact Form - PublishPress'=>'Fọọmu Ibaṣepọ - PublishPress','Count Up - PublishPress'=>'Ka Soke - PublishPress','Images Slider - PublishPress'=>'Aworan Slider - PublishPress','Info Box - PublishPress'=>'Apoti Alaye - PublishPress','Map - PublishPress'=>'Maapu - PublishPress','Newsletter - PublishPress'=>'Iwe iroyin - PublishPress','Social Links - Pu