                                            (usually set this same as the custom style\'s background color)'=>'Aṣayan yii ṣe iranlọwọ fun ọ lati ṣe idanimọ awọn aṣa aṣa pato ninu atokọ
                                            (nigbagbogbo ṣeto eyi ni kanna bi awọ abẹlẹ aṣa)','Identification color'=>'Awọ idanimọ','Style Builder'=>'Olùkó àṣà','Custom CSS'=>'CSS Aṣa','Hint: Use "Ctrl + Space" for auto completion'=>'Iṣeduro: Lo "Ctrl + Space" fun ipari aifọwọyi','Headings'=>'Awọn akọle','Links'=>'Awọn ọna asopọ','Media'=>'Media','Containers'=>'Awọn apoti','Interactive'=>'Ibi iṣẹ','Save styles'=>'Fipamọ awọn aṣa','You can control who can use each block, including default WordPress blocks.'=>'O le ṣakoso ẹni ti o le lo ọkọọkan awọn bulọọki, pẹlu awọn bulọọki WordPress aiyipada.','Enable extra blocks including content displays, sliders, buttons, icons, tabs, accordions, and more.'=>'Mu awọn bulọọki afikun ṣiṣẹ pẹlu awọn ifihan akoonu, awọn olutọpa, awọn bọtini, awọn aami, awọn taabu, awọn akordeon, ati diẹ sii.','You can add your own CSS styles for your blocks. Anyone editing posts can quickly add the styles to blocks.'=>'O le fi awọn aṣa CSS ti tirẹ kun fun awọn bulọọki rẹ. Ẹnikẹni ti o n ṣatunkọ awọn ifiweranṣẹ le ni kiakia ṣafikun awọn aṣa si awọn bulọọki.','This feature adds display controls for blocks. You can schedule when blocks are shown, and add user role restrictions.'=>'Iṣẹ yii nfi awọn iṣakoso ifihan kun fun awọn bulọọki. O le ṣeto nigbati awọn bulọọki han, ati fi awọn ihamọ ipa olumulo kun.','You can scan the posts on your website for blocks usage.'=>'O le ṣawari awọn ifiweranṣẹ lori oju opo wẹẹbu rẹ fun lilo awọn bulọọki.','This feature enables a submenu to manage your Reusable Blocks.'=>'Ẹya yii n mu submenu wa lati ṣakoso Awọn Bulọọki Tuntun rẹ.','Automatically insert reusable blocks into posts based on position, categories, tags, and other criteria.'=>'Fi awọn bulọọki ti a tun lo laifọwọyi sinu awọn ifiweranṣẹ da lori ipo, awọn ẹka, awọn aami, ati awọn itọkasi miiran.','Core Blocks Features'=>'Awọn ẹya Bulọọki Pataki','Add Google Fonts support to core blocks including paragraphs and headings.'=>'Fi atilẹyin Fonts Google kun si awọn bulọọki pataki pẹlu awọn paragirafi ati awọn akọle.','Block Features'=>'Awọn ẹya Bulọọki','Maps'=>'Awọn maapu','Email & Forms'=>'Imeeli & Awọn fọọmu','reCAPTCHA'=>'reCAPTCHA','Data Export'=>'Gbigbe Data','License'=>'Iwe-aṣẹ','Select Role'=>'Yan Ipa','Disable all block adding'=>'Dena gbogbo fifi bulọọki kun','Prevent users in %1s role from adding new block to posts.'=>'Ṣe idiwọ awọn olumulo ninu ipa %1s lati fi bulọọki tuntun kun si awọn ifiweranṣẹ.','Disable the Pattern Directory'=>'Dena Awọn itọsọna Àpẹẹrẹ','Disable the pattern directory for users in %1s role.'=>'Pa ọna àkọsílẹ́ fún àwọn olumulo ní ipa %1s.','Disable the Openverse'=>'Pa Openverse','Disable Openverse for users in %1s role.'=>'Pa Openverse fún àwọn olumulo ní ipa %1s.','Save Image Settings'=>'Fipamọ́ Àwọn Eto Àwòrán','Download Contacts Form data'=>'Gbigba data Fọọmu Awọn olubasọrọ','Data stored through Contact form blocks.'=>'Data tí a fipamọ́ nipasẹ awọn bulọọki fọọmu olubasọrọ.','CSV'=>'CSV','JSON'=>'JSON','Download Newsletter Form data'=>'Gbigba data Fọọmu Iwe iroyin','Data stored through Newsletter form blocks.'=>'Data tí a fipamọ́ nipasẹ awọn bulọọki fọọmu iwe iroyin.','These email settings apply to messages sent through PublishPress Contact form block.'=>'Awọn eto imeeli wọnyi lo si awọn ifiranṣẹ ti a firanṣẹ nipasẹ bulọọki fọọmu olubasọrọ PublishPress.','Sender name'=>'Orukọ oluranse','Sender email'=>'Imeeli oluranse','Email title'=>'Akọle imeeli','Email receiver'=>'Olugba imeeli','Save Form Settings'=>'Fipamọ́ Àwọn Eto Fọọmu','Display PublishPress branding'=>'Fihan ami iyasọtọ PublishPress','PublishPress logo and links in the footer of the admin pages'=>'Ami PublishPress ati awọn ìjápọ̀ ní ipari awọn oju-iwe alakoso','Enable blocks spacing'=>'Mu aaye awọn bulọọki ṣiṣẹ','Vertical spacing between blocks'=>'Ibi tí ó gíga láàárín awọn bulọọki','Blocks spacing'=>'Ibi ààlà àwọn bulọọki','Blocks icon color'=>'Àwọ́ àwòrán bulọọki','Apply in admin to blocks from PublishPress Blocks plugin.'=>'Lo ninu iṣakoso si awọn bulọọki lati PublishPress Blocks plugin.','Gutenberg editor width'=>'Iwọn olootu Gutenberg','Large'=>'Nla','Enable columns visual guide'=>'Mú itọsọna àwòrán àpò-ọpọlọ ṣiṣẹ','Visual guide for PublishPress Blocks Columns block'=>'Itọsọna àwòrán fun PublishPress Bulọọki Àwọn Bulọọki','Remove autop'=>'Yọ autop','Autop WordPress function is used to prevent unwanted paragraphs to be added'=>'Iṣẹ autop WordPress ni a lo lati ṣe idiwọ awọn paragirafi ti a ko fẹ lati wa ni afikun','Save General Settings'=>'Fipamọ Eto Gbogbogbo','Open galleries in lightbox'=>'Ṣí àwọn àwòrán àwòrán ni lightbox','Open gallery images as a lightbox style popup'=>'Ṣí awọn aworan àwòrán gẹgẹbi popup aṣa lightbox','Image caption'=>'Àkíyèsí aworan','Disabled'=>'Ti pa','Overlay'=>'Ẹ̀ka àfihàn','Display caption text on images loaded as lightbox in galleries.'=>'Fihan ọrọ àkíyèsí lori awọn aworan ti a gbe wọle gẹgẹbi lightbox ni awọn àwòrán àwòrán.','Default thumbnail'=>'Àtọkànwá àwòrán kekere','Reset to default'=>'Tun ṣeto si àtọkànwá','Set the default post thumbnail to use in Content Display blocks for posts without featured image.'=>'Ṣeto aworan akọsilẹ ifiweranṣẹ aiyipada lati lo ninu awọn bulọọki Ifihan Akoonu fun awọn ifiweranṣẹ laisi aworan ti a ṣe afihan.','Google API key'=>'Bọtini Google API','How to create a Google API Key'=>'Báwo ni a ṣe lè dá Google API Key ṣẹ','A Google API key is required to use the Map block without any warning.'=>'A nilo Google API key lati lo àpótí Map láìṣe ìkìlọ̀ kankan.','Save Maps Settings'=>'Fipamọ́ Àtọ́kànwá Maps','Use the Google reCAPTCHA to avoid spam in PublishPress Blocks forms. Get credentials for your domain by registering %shere%s.'=>'Lo Google reCAPTCHA lati yago fun spam ni awọn fọọmu PublishPress Blocks. Gba awọn iwe-ẹri fun agbegbe rẹ nipa iforukọsilẹ %shere%s.','Enable reCAPTCHA'=>'Mú reCAPTCHA ṣiṣẹ','Site key'=>'Bọtìnì aaye','required'=>'nilo','Secret key'=>'Bọtìnì aṣírí','Language'=>'Èdè','Auto detect'=>'Ìmúlẹ̀ àautomátíkì','Language codes list'=>'Àtòjọ kóòdù èdè','Theme'=>'Kíkọ́','Light'=>'Fọ́tò','Invisible'=>'Kò hàn','We strongly recommend not using Invisible reCAPTCHA if you have more than 1 Newsletter or Contact forms block in a page.'=>'A ni imọran gidigidi pe ki o ma lo Invisible reCAPTCHA ti o ba ni diẹ sii ju 1 bulọọki Iwe iroyin tabi Fọọmu olubasọrọ ninu oju-iwe kan.','Save reCAPTCHA Settings'=>'Fipamọ́ Àtọ́kànwá reCAPTCHA','Countdown'=>'Ìkànsí','Easily create a customizable countdown.'=>'Rọrun láti dá ìkànsí kan ti a lè ṣe àtúnṣe.','Pricing Table'=>'Tábìlì Iye','Easily create a customizable pricing table.'=>'Rọrun láti dá tábìlì iye kan ti a lè ṣe àtúnṣe.','Feature'=>'Àmì','Use block to create a list inside the Feature List" block.'=>'Lo àkóónú láti dá àkójọpọ̀ nínú àkóónú Àmì" àkóónú.','Feature List'=>'Àkójọpọ̀ Àmì','Gutenberg is not detected! Activate it or'=>'Gutenberg kò rí! Mu un ṣiṣẹ́ tàbí','Install Gutenberg Now!'=>'Fi Gutenberg sílẹ̀ Ní báyìí!','We require at least Gutenberg version '=>'A nílò o kere ju ẹya Gutenberg ','Please update Gutenberg then comeback later!'=>'Jọ̀wọ́ ṣe imudojuiwọn Gutenberg lẹ́yìn náà padà wa!','M'=>'M','W'=>'W','F'=>'F','accordion'=>'accordion','faq'=>'faq','Groove'=>'Groove','Ridge'=>'Ridge','Inset'=>'Inset','Outset'=>'Outset','Padding top'=>'Padding top','Minus 2'=>'Minus 2','Plus 2'=>'Plus 2','data'=>'data','Stripes'=>'Stripes','HTML Anchor'=>'HTML Anchor','tab'=>'tab','media'=>'media','50 / 50'=>'50 / 50','66 / 33'=>'66 / 33','33 / 66'=>'33 / 66','25 / 75'=>'25 / 75','75 / 25'=>'75 / 25','20 / 80'=>'20 / 80','80 / 20'=>'80 / 20','33 / 33 / 33'=>'33 / 33 / 33','50 / 25 / 25'=>'50 / 25 / 25','25 / 25 / 50'=>'25 / 25 / 50','25 / 50 / 25'=>'25 / 50 / 25','20 / 60 / 20'=>'20 / 60 / 20','60 / 20 / 20'=>'60 / 20 / 20','20 / 20 / 60'=>'20 / 20 / 60','16.6 / 66.6 / 16.6'=>'16.6 / 66.6 / 16.6','25 / 25 / 25 / 25'=>'25 / 25 / 25 / 25','50 / 16.6 / 16.6 / 16.6'=>'50 / 16.6 / 16.6 / 16.6','16.6 / 16.6 / 16.6 / 50'=>'16.6 / 16.6 / 16.6 / 50','20 / 20 / 20 / 40'=>'